These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, board-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, pilot
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, mystery
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, nigerian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, tram
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the pilot is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the owner of the lizard is the nigerian##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | soy-milk       |
| Hobby         | fishing   | board-games     |
| Job           | dressmaker | pilot   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | action  |
| Nationality   | nigerian | thai |
| Pet           | lizard      | rabbit     |
| Transport     | tram    | trike   |

