.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, electrician
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, blues
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, russian
2 different pets are kept: frog, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter
1. the electrician is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the owner of the pony is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the russian is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | sprite |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing        | chess  |
| Job           | musician | electrician  |
| Music-Genre   | blues            | house    |
| Nationality   | colombian     | russian   |
| Pet           | frog         | pony    |
| Transport     | scooter           | helicopter      |

